@PaulHigin I've included a sanitized copy of the module and JEA config. I am using an AD group managed service account for this JEA config.

I do see the issue if I create the JEA configuration endpoint on the same local machine, and then connect to it. The event logs seem to indicate it is a registration time problem, not a connectivity issue where local vs not would be an issue.
